        <para id="id7857047">Be a chef: Develop your own recipe for chocolate biscuits. Use melted chocolate, some coconut, green and red cherries, nuts and breakfast cereal made from maize, e.g. Cornflakes. Be sure to have the help of an adult when you melt the chocolate. </para>
